      "span_text": "A questionnaire concerning expectations, motivation and satisfaction with regard to RTS was constructed. This questionnaire contains 15 questions divided over three dimensions: Expectations (9 questions), Motivation (3 questions) and Satisfaction (3 questions) based on the questionnaire by Sonneson & Ardern (2016) [CITATION_1] ."
